ComboStepAction: The action that must be completed (according to Combo Step Completion States) to progress the combo
ComboStepCompletionStates: Trigger events that will complete this step - what events from this action should progress the combo
TimeToPressKey:
Time to press the key before combo is cancelled - starts once the previous step in the combo is completed
Note: This can be safely ignored for the first action in the combo
